<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Booking</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="stylesheets/style.css"/>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Current directory views/pages -->
    <main class="booking_page">

        <section class="top_container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>FACE2UNE</h1>
                <a href="">Log in</a> 
            </div>
            <ol class="progress">
                <li class="active step-container">Choose Appointment</li>
                <li class="step-container">Your info</li>
                <li class="step-container">Confirmation</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="appointments">
            <div class="button_container">
                <button class="bubbly-button">USE MY CODE</button>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment">
                <div class="appointment_body">
                    <div class="appointment_header">
                        <p1>BACK TO BASICS</p1>
                        <p2>30 minutes @ €55.00</p2>
                        <button class="bubbly-button" id="book_btn">BOOK</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="appointment_description">
                        <span>The Signature manual sculpting technique, suitable for anyone. The basic need to sustain youthful look & plump, radiant skin. / Le modelage manuel signature convient à tout. La base fondamentale pour conserver une appearance jeune et une peau pulpeuse et radieuse.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="book_modal" class="modal">
                        <div class="modal_book_content">
                            <button class="x" id="close_modal">&times;</button>
                            <div class="modal_book_header">
                                <h1>Your appointment:</h1>
                               
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>    
        
    </main>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.js"></script>
<script src = "javascripts/slick.min.js"></script>
<script src = "javascripts/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>